1
00:00:07,100 --> 00:00:08,230
<font color="yellow">My father...</font>

2
00:00:10,130 --> 00:00:12,000
<font color="yellow">has six months to live.</font>

3
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:18,960
<font color="yellow">Before he passes away,</font>

4
00:00:19,730 --> 00:00:20,930
<font color="yellow">marry me.</font>

5
00:00:23,860 --> 00:00:25,160
<font color="yellow">If you can't marry me,</font>

6
00:00:25,730 --> 00:00:27,030
<font color="yellow">let's get engaged at least.</font>

7
00:00:37,060 --> 00:00:38,160
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:42,660
<font color="yellow">Are you sure you won't regret it?</font>

9
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:49,130
<font color="yellow">You might not be happy...</font>

10
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:52,430
<font color="yellow">if you marry me.</font>

11
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:54,400
<font color="yellow">All I need is you.</font>

12
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:57,000
<font color="yellow">That's enough...</font>

13
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:00,230
<font color="yellow">for me to be happy.</font>

14
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,430
<font color="yellow">Don't think about anything else.</font>

15
00:01:20,630 --> 00:01:21,760
<font color="yellow">Please be brave for me...</font>

16
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,660
<font color="yellow">just this once.</font>

17
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,730
<font color="yellow">Can you...</font>

18
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,000
<font color="yellow">give me some time?</font>

19
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:34,030
<font color="yellow">It won't take long.</font>

20
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:38,400
<font color="yellow">All right. I'll be waiting for you.</font>

21
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:47,660
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

22
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:52,900
<font color="yellow">Don't be so upset...</font>

23
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,900
<font color="yellow">about what happened to the chairman.</font>

24
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,530
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Soo Yeon.</font>

25
00:02:20,830 --> 00:02:21,900
<font color="yellow">(Episode 42)</font>

26
00:02:22,230 --> 00:02:23,700
<font color="yellow">It's an agreement...</font>

27
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:26,630
<font color="yellow">to show that Z Capital will be under both of our names.</font>

28
00:02:29,860 --> 00:02:31,300
<font color="yellow">(Joint Name Contract)</font>

29
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:42,830
<font color="yellow">(Do Gun Woo)</font>

30
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:53,160
<font color="yellow">With that, we're now partners.</font>

31
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:56,530
<font color="yellow">When will we terminate the agreement?</font>

32
00:02:56,530 --> 00:02:58,100
<font color="yellow">Once Gi Tan is eliminated.</font>

33
00:02:58,860 --> 00:02:59,960
<font color="yellow">You better...</font>

34
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:03,060
<font color="yellow">hand over the copies of my documents.</font>

35
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:18,200
<font color="yellow">You didn't make more copies, did you?</font>

36
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,930
<font color="yellow">We have to trust each other from now on.</font>

37
00:03:19,930 --> 00:03:22,530
<font color="yellow">If we break the trust, we can't be partners any more.</font>

38
00:03:24,130 --> 00:03:28,030
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon won't be please to find your working with me.</font>

39
00:03:29,730 --> 00:03:31,730
<font color="yellow">I'm not trying to threaten you.</font>

40
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,560
<font color="yellow">I'm just worried, that's all.</font>

41
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:36,830
<font color="yellow">If you dare mention this to her, you won't be able to use...</font>

42
00:03:36,830 --> 00:03:38,530
<font color="yellow">any money from the Z Capital account.</font>

43
00:03:41,130 --> 00:03:43,100
<font color="yellow">If you try to get in my way,</font>

44
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:47,230
<font color="yellow">I'll show this contract to Soo Yeon.</font>

45
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:53,260
<font color="yellow">You might think that you've tied me down, but I don't think so.</font>

46
00:03:54,660 --> 00:03:55,900
<font color="yellow">This agreement...</font>

47
00:03:56,530 --> 00:04:00,360
<font color="yellow">will make our relationship stronger.</font>

48
00:04:14,930 --> 00:04:18,860
<font color="yellow">What's gotten into you? Why did you ask me out for drinks?</font>

49
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:25,030
<font color="yellow">Good timing. I had to talk to you about Dad anyway.</font>

50
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:28,960
<font color="yellow">You have no idea what's going on with the inheritance do you?</font>

51
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,100
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, that jerk,</font>

52
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:35,270
<font color="yellow">is using Dad's sickness as an excuse...</font>

53
00:04:37,330 --> 00:04:41,630
<font color="yellow">Listen carefully because I won't treat you like a brother any more.</font>

54
00:04:44,270 --> 00:04:46,030
<font color="yellow">What's wrong? Are you drunk already?</font>

55
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:50,480
<font color="yellow">I don't care what Gun Woo did to Gi Tan. It's not my problem.</font>

56
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,830
<font color="yellow">However, it's different with you...</font>

57
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:55,830
<font color="yellow">because you were my brother.</font>

58
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,560
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

59
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,330
<font color="yellow">Shin Young.</font>

60
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,560
<font color="yellow">Murderer.</font>

61
00:05:03,030 --> 00:05:04,130
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

62
00:05:04,730 --> 00:05:07,270
<font color="yellow">I know you killed Gi Tan's parents.</font>

63
00:05:08,770 --> 00:05:10,330
<font color="yellow">Whom did you hear that from?</font>

64
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:12,770
<font color="yellow">Did Gi Tan say that?</font>

65
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:15,700
<font color="yellow">Don't expect anything from me from now on.</font>

66
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,460
<font color="yellow">This is the end between us.</font>

67
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,330
<font color="yellow">If we're no longer family,</font>

68
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:29,000
<font color="yellow">do you think it'll work out between you and Gi Tan?</font>

69
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,830
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

70
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:33,900
<font color="yellow">Don't be so stupid.</font>

71
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:35,730
<font color="yellow">Even if you try,</font>

72
00:05:36,260 --> 00:05:37,700
<font color="yellow">I'm still your brother.</font>

73
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,760
<font color="yellow">Why do you think I did that?</font>

74
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:43,360
<font color="yellow">I did it to save our company.</font>

75
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:46,420
<font color="yellow">It wasn't for me. I did it for Dad and Dodo Group!</font>

76
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:48,260
<font color="yellow">Do you call that an excuse?</font>

77
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:49,300
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

78
00:05:51,130 --> 00:05:54,400
<font color="yellow">Why would I make an excuse to you?</font>

79
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:56,730
<font color="yellow">Also,</font>

80
00:05:57,360 --> 00:06:00,760
<font color="yellow">I'm not scared even if you're no longer my family. But!</font>

81
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,960
<font color="yellow">Remember this one thing.</font>

82
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,900
<font color="yellow">You're nothing to Gi Tan.</font>

83
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:13,960
<font color="yellow">He'll only use you like me.</font>

84
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:18,200
<font color="yellow">All the sins and debt you've committed and owe to Gi Tan...</font>

85
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:20,600
<font color="yellow">I'll repay them all.</font>

86
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:24,560
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

87
00:06:25,730 --> 00:06:28,330
<font color="yellow">don't mind me and lead a proper life.</font>

88
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:53,760
<font color="yellow">Sir! Sir!</font>

89
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:57,160
<font color="yellow">Have you seen CEO Do?</font>

90
00:06:58,130 --> 00:06:59,160
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

91
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:02,100
<font color="yellow">She missed her meeting and she's not picking up her phone.</font>

92
00:07:02,530 --> 00:07:03,760
<font color="yellow">I'm a little worried.</font>

93
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,530
<font color="yellow">Maybe she went to the bathhouse.</font>

94
00:07:05,530 --> 00:07:09,100
<font color="yellow">She didn't say a word today and seemed down.</font>

95
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:12,230
<font color="yellow">Shin Young can look sad?</font>

96
00:07:12,230 --> 00:07:13,300
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

97
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,000
<font color="yellow">(Kang Ga Din)</font>

98
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:45,400
<font color="yellow">Kang Ga Din. Did you get my telepathy?</font>

99
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:48,700
<font color="yellow">I was just thinking about you, too.</font>

100
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:51,430
<font color="yellow">- Are you drinking right now?
-  Yes.</font>

101
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:54,360
<font color="yellow">I'm really craving drinks today.</font>

102
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:55,900
<font color="yellow">Whom are you with?</font>

103
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,730
<font color="yellow">With a handsome man.</font>

104
00:07:59,730 --> 00:08:02,630
<font color="yellow">- Where are you right now?
-  At a cart bar near the hotel.</font>

105
00:08:03,330 --> 00:08:05,630
<font color="yellow">Why do you ask? Are you going to take me home?</font>

106
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:08,560
<font color="yellow">Are you crazy? Why would I go when you're drinking with a guy?</font>

107
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:10,530
<font color="yellow">Right.</font>

108
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:12,530
<font color="yellow">Don't come.</font>

109
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:14,430
<font color="yellow">I don't need you to come.</font>

110
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:18,360
<font color="yellow">Nothing happened, right?</font>

111
00:08:22,030 --> 00:08:25,660
<font color="yellow">This guy tells me he really likes me. What should I do?</font>

112
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:29,330
<font color="yellow">Good luck. Don't get too drunk though.</font>

113
00:08:31,260 --> 00:08:34,000
<font color="yellow">I knew she'd pick up your call.</font>

114
00:08:34,330 --> 00:08:37,130
<font color="yellow">She says she's drinking with a guy. Don't worry.</font>

115
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:40,160
<font color="yellow">With a guy? That's impossible.</font>

116
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:41,900
<font color="yellow">It's not like she'd drink alone.</font>

117
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:48,370
<font color="yellow">Gosh. Why is she worrying me?</font>

118
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:50,290
<font color="yellow">Are you going?</font>

119
00:08:50,290 --> 00:08:52,630
<font color="yellow">What if she's drunk again?</font>

120
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:08,870
<font color="yellow">Kang Gi Tan!</font>

121
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:15,800
<font color="yellow">Why did you come? I told you not to.</font>

122
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:19,100
<font color="yellow">What happened to your date?</font>

123
00:09:20,830 --> 00:09:23,260
<font color="yellow">He's right here. Inside me.</font>

124
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,230
<font color="yellow">Why are you drinking by yourself?</font>

125
00:09:30,060 --> 00:09:31,600
<font color="yellow">Don't look at me like that. It makes me nervous.</font>

126
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:34,370
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Gi Tan.</font>

127
00:09:35,330 --> 00:09:36,460
<font color="yellow">For what?</font>

128
00:09:39,130 --> 00:09:40,200
<font color="yellow">Just...</font>

129
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,370
<font color="yellow">Everything.</font>

130
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:44,500
<font color="yellow">Is this your new drinking habit?</font>

131
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:50,630
<font color="yellow">I won't ever get drunk again in front of you...</font>

132
00:09:51,370 --> 00:09:53,800
<font color="yellow">and I won't do anything that you don't like.</font>

133
00:10:05,370 --> 00:10:06,460
<font color="yellow">Shin Young.</font>

134
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:10,130
<font color="yellow">Do you know what's so attractive about you?</font>

135
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:13,030
<font color="yellow">Being confident.</font>

136
00:10:14,370 --> 00:10:16,500
<font color="yellow">It doesn't matter whom you're with and where you are.</font>

137
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:18,730
<font color="yellow">You're always confident and never discouraged.</font>

138
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,430
<font color="yellow">That's your charm.</font>

139
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:27,060
<font color="yellow">So don't say things like you're sorry. Okay?</font>

140
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,330
<font color="yellow">You're Do Shin Young.</font>

141
00:10:35,530 --> 00:10:36,700
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

142
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:40,230
<font color="yellow">I'll do everything you say.</font>

143
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,800
<font color="yellow">We'll get busy starting tomorrow.</font>

144
00:10:48,330 --> 00:10:49,700
<font color="yellow">So let's drink today...</font>

145
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:52,660
<font color="yellow">and start working hard from tomorrow.</font>

146
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,860
<font color="yellow">(Dodo Group)</font>

147
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,400
<font color="yellow">Yes, Mr Gong.</font>

148
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:21,060
<font color="yellow">The chairman's condition is getting worse.</font>

149
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:24,860
<font color="yellow">I think we should get him to a hospital.</font>

150
00:11:25,430 --> 00:11:26,800
<font color="yellow">I'll go home right now.</font>

151
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:34,530
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Uncle.</font>

152
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:38,890
<font color="yellow">Of course. I'll get him diagnosed incompetent...</font>

153
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:41,960
<font color="yellow">to completely destroy Gun Woo.</font>

154
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,400
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

155
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,960
<font color="yellow">What did he say?</font>

156
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:51,260
<font color="yellow">A doctor was just sent from the court to diagnose him.</font>

157
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,730
<font color="yellow">Ji Soo,</font>

158
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:54,590
<font color="yellow">can you take Mum home?</font>

159
00:11:54,590 --> 00:11:57,000
<font color="yellow">Why would I go there? You should go.</font>

160
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,960
<font color="yellow">I have to talk to someone from the court today.</font>

161
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:02,380
<font color="yellow">I need to get our restraining order lifted.</font>

162
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:03,960
<font color="yellow">How would you lift that?</font>

163
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:06,750
<font color="yellow">Hey, are you looking down on him right now?</font>

164
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,800
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

165
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:10,130
<font color="yellow">I'm not looking down on him.</font>

166
00:12:10,130 --> 00:12:11,560
<font color="yellow">Stop complaining and come right out.</font>

167
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:23,300
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

168
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:28,230
<font color="yellow">You won't last much longer.</font>

169
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,040
<font color="yellow">Is he doing very bad?</font>

170
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:51,490
<font color="yellow">Yes. He's much worse today.</font>

171
00:12:51,490 --> 00:12:52,500
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong.</font>

172
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:56,060
<font color="yellow">Who's this?</font>

173
00:12:57,500 --> 00:13:00,500
<font color="yellow">He doesn't recognise you, so make something up.</font>

174
00:13:03,130 --> 00:13:04,230
<font color="yellow">I am...</font>

175
00:13:04,700 --> 00:13:06,360
<font color="yellow">your new assistant as of today.</font>

176
00:13:08,700 --> 00:13:09,700
<font color="yellow">My assistant?</font>

177
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:13,000
<font color="yellow">Did you hire him?</font>

178
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:14,530
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

179
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:19,130
<font color="yellow">He looks like someone I know.</font>

180
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:23,100
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

181
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:26,130
<font color="yellow">Why aren't we getting ready to go to Mr Hwang's house?</font>

182
00:13:26,530 --> 00:13:29,130
<font color="yellow">- Pardon?
-  I want to go see Gwi Ja.</font>

183
00:13:31,300 --> 00:13:35,030
<font color="yellow">He's been looking for her since early in the morning.</font>

184
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:37,160
<font color="yellow">We should just let him see her.</font>

185
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,460
<font color="yellow">Let's get him to the hospital.</font>

186
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:39,900
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

187
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,960
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

188
00:13:42,530 --> 00:13:44,380
<font color="yellow">Let's get dressed...</font>

189
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:45,990
<font color="yellow">so we can go and see Mrs Hwang.</font>

190
00:13:45,990 --> 00:13:47,760
<font color="yellow">- Sure.
-  Okay.</font>

191
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:07,360
<font color="yellow">- Mrs Hwang.
-  Who are you people?</font>

192
00:14:08,300 --> 00:14:10,480
<font color="yellow">They are here to diagnose him on a court order...</font>

193
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:12,500
<font color="yellow">to announce your father as incompetent.</font>

194
00:14:20,260 --> 00:14:21,480
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

195
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,500
<font color="yellow">It's me.</font>

196
00:14:23,300 --> 00:14:24,300
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong.</font>

197
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:26,830
<font color="yellow">When did you hire...</font>

198
00:14:27,330 --> 00:14:28,860
<font color="yellow">a new housekeeper?</font>

199
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:31,260
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

200
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,960
<font color="yellow">You don't even...</font>

201
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:35,900
<font color="yellow">recognise me any more.</font>

202
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:38,800
<font color="yellow">He recognised you last time.</font>

203
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:41,900
<font color="yellow">Get out of here. You're on a restraining order so...</font>

204
00:14:45,330 --> 00:14:47,800
<font color="yellow">Did you think I wouldn't know that he has dementia?</font>

205
00:14:49,130 --> 00:14:50,160
<font color="yellow">Excuse me.</font>

206
00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:53,630
<font color="yellow">He's my new assistant.</font>

207
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,630
<font color="yellow">Did he do something wrong?</font>

208
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:00,270
<font color="yellow">This is definite.</font>

209
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:02,700
<font color="yellow">He doesn't recognise his wife and calls his son his assistant.</font>

210
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,460
<font color="yellow">Diagnose him with dementia.</font>

211
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:06,130
<font color="yellow">Yes, Ma'am.</font>

212
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,300
<font color="yellow">Take him and go.</font>

213
00:15:16,700 --> 00:15:19,570
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong, Gwi Ja loves cake.</font>

214
00:15:19,570 --> 00:15:21,060
<font color="yellow">We should get some on our way.</font>

215
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:22,660
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

216
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:31,660
<font color="yellow">I never hid the fact that he has dementia.</font>

