00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:33,980
<font color="yellow">Stop lying.</font>

218
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:35,650
<font color="yellow">I already heard from Dr Hwang.</font>

219
00:15:35,650 --> 00:15:38,000
<font color="yellow">I just didn't see the need to tell you people.</font>

