00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,260
<font color="yellow">Of course you needed to.</font>

221
00:15:40,060 --> 00:15:42,930
<font color="yellow">Your father wrote his will before he met you.</font>

222
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:45,800
<font color="yellow">You hid his illness because you knew you didn't have a part in his will.</font>

223
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:48,460
<font color="yellow">You're just like your mother.</font>

224
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:52,700
<font color="yellow">You're a liar and are good at stabbing someone's back.</font>

225
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:54,800
<font color="yellow">Let's go, Ji Soo.</font>

226
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:02,830
<font color="yellow">What happened...</font>

227
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:05,200
<font color="yellow">to finding someone who can write like Father?</font>

228
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,160
<font color="yellow">I found someone.</font>

229
00:16:21,530 --> 00:16:23,230
<font color="yellow">What are you trying to do?</font>

230
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,580
<font color="yellow">Meals here aren't that great.</font>

231
00:16:25,580 --> 00:16:26,880
<font color="yellow">Everything here was...</font>

232
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:30,850
<font color="yellow">made by Lawyer Oh at home. They're very good.</font>

233
00:16:30,850 --> 00:16:31,900
<font color="yellow">Have some.</font>

234
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:34,800
<font color="yellow">Il Jae never came to visit, did he?</font>

235
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:37,160
<font color="yellow">I never saw his name on your records.</font>

236
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:38,630
<font color="yellow">Dream all you like.</font>

237
00:16:39,060 --> 00:16:40,530
<font color="yellow">I will never betray him.</font>

238
00:16:40,530 --> 00:16:44,000
<font color="yellow">My goodness. If you were this loyal in the army,</font>

239
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,400
<font color="yellow">you'd be a general by now.</font>

240
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:49,160
<font color="yellow">Instead, you came to prison to rot because of Il Jae.</font>

241
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:53,060
<font color="yellow">I told Il Jae that I'm meeting you.</font>

242
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:58,100
<font color="yellow">I told him how you wouldn't give in, and he seemed very pleased.</font>

243
00:16:58,660 --> 00:16:59,730
<font color="yellow">But he is...</font>

244
00:16:59,730 --> 00:17:02,600
<font color="yellow">suspicious about everything.</font>

245
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,980
<font color="yellow">I'm not sure if this will be all right.</font>

246
00:17:04,980 --> 00:17:07,000
<font color="yellow">We're going to come every day.</font>

247
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,680
<font color="yellow">If you'd like a specific dish, you can tell me.</font>

248
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:09,760
<font color="yellow">Oh Soo Yeon.</font>

249
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,300
<font color="yellow">If you don't want to see me,</font>

250
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:14,260
<font color="yellow">tell me at least where the doctor...</font>

251
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:16,530
<font color="yellow">who performed Dong Soo's autopsy is hiding.</font>

252
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:18,330
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'll tell you?</font>

253
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:22,330
<font color="yellow">- That means you do know.
-  Exactly.</font>

254
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:24,130
<font color="yellow">He does know.</font>

255
00:17:30,330 --> 00:17:32,570
<font color="yellow">Do you have anything that you like in particular?</font>

256
00:17:33,130 --> 00:17:36,600
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh is good at cooking meat dishes.</font>

257
00:17:36,600 --> 00:17:37,600
<font color="yellow">Do you think...</font>

258
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:39,700
<font color="yellow">you can persuade me with this?</font>

259
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,570
<font color="yellow">I have to try anything.</font>

260
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,280
<font color="yellow">If you were me,</font>

261
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:46,400
<font color="yellow">would you just sit around when your brother died a wrongful death?</font>

262
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:51,160
<font color="yellow">I'll be back tomorrow.</font>

263
00:17:52,030 --> 00:17:53,700
<font color="yellow">You can take your time and eat them all.</font>

264
00:17:57,230 --> 00:18:01,100
<font color="yellow">Come on. Eat up. They look great.</font>

265
00:18:03,030 --> 00:18:05,100
<font color="yellow">If you don't eat everything, I'll sue you.</font>

266
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,630
<font color="yellow">The chairman's writing is on the right...</font>

267
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:25,860
<font color="yellow">and the left is a copy of his handwriting.</font>

268
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,400
<font color="yellow">Put them together.</font>

269
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,840
<font color="yellow">There are small differences.</font>

270
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:40,390
<font color="yellow">Experts say they are 90 percent identical.</font>

271
00:18:40,390 --> 00:18:41,730
<font color="yellow">How long until 100 percent?</font>

272
00:18:41,730 --> 00:18:43,680
<font color="yellow">One more week.</font>

273
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,760
<font color="yellow">Once it's finished,</font>

274
00:18:45,300 --> 00:18:47,070
<font color="yellow">let handwriting experts take a look.</font>

275
00:18:47,530 --> 00:18:48,530
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

276
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:52,280
<font color="yellow">Once I have Father's handwritten will,</font>

277
00:18:52,280 --> 00:18:54,570
<font color="yellow">it wouldn't matter even if he's declared incompetent.</font>

278
00:19:06,130 --> 00:19:08,400
<font color="yellow">You're really late. I told you to be on time.</font>

279
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:12,860
<font color="yellow">I'm not that late.</font>

280
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:14,030
<font color="yellow">We're late. Let's go.</font>

281
00:19:14,530 --> 00:19:15,530
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

282
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:18,130
<font color="yellow">Where are we going?</font>

283
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,760
<font color="yellow">Do you remember Chainsaw So?</font>

284
00:19:21,330 --> 00:19:23,030
<font color="yellow">He's going to hand me his matured bonds.</font>

285
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:26,570
<font color="yellow">It's a very important meeting. Do not make any mistakes.</font>

286
00:19:34,660 --> 00:19:37,730
<font color="yellow">To Gi Tan, you're nothing but a family member of his enemy.</font>

287
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:40,500
<font color="yellow">He'll just use you...</font>

288
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:43,130
<font color="yellow">and leave you in misery.</font>

289
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:57,860
<font color="yellow">Say hello. This is Chainsaw...</font>

290
00:19:59,230 --> 00:20:00,260
<font color="yellow">I mean,</font>

291
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:02,700
<font color="yellow">Chairman So Gil Du.</font>

292
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:06,860
<font color="yellow">I'm Do Shin Young, Dodo Hotel's CEO.</font>

293
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:12,780
<font color="yellow">I heard Chairman Do had a shrew for a daughter.</font>

294
00:20:12,780 --> 00:20:13,940
<font color="yellow">That must be you.</font>

295
00:20:13,940 --> 00:20:15,300
<font color="yellow">A shrew?</font>

296
00:20:15,300 --> 00:20:16,430
<font color="yellow">Do I look like a shrew?</font>

297
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:18,530
<font color="yellow">Hey, Shin Young.</font>

298
00:20:20,430 --> 00:20:21,430
<font color="yellow">Sit.</font>

299
00:20:30,430 --> 00:20:31,670
<font color="yellow">Why did you...</font>

300
00:20:31,670 --> 00:20:33,730
<font color="yellow">bring this girl?</font>

301
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,460
<font color="yellow">Shin Young...</font>

302
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:39,130
<font color="yellow">will be the next chairwoman of Dodo Group.</font>

303
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:42,720
<font color="yellow">The next chairwoman?</font>

304
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:45,660
<font color="yellow">We plan on changing the holding company of Dodo Group...</font>

305
00:20:46,730 --> 00:20:48,330
<font color="yellow">from Dodo Pharmaceutical to Dodo Hotel.</font>

306
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:51,730
<font color="yellow">Is that the best...</font>

307
00:20:51,730 --> 00:20:54,000
<font color="yellow">you came up with by using my bonds?</font>

308
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:57,860
<font color="yellow">Ms Do and I have signed a shareholders' voting agreement.</font>

309
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:01,930
<font color="yellow">I'll be participating in Dodo Group's management.</font>

310
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:03,760
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

311
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:06,430
<font color="yellow">How much bonds did you get so far?</font>

312
00:21:06,430 --> 00:21:08,800
<font color="yellow">It's really nothing compared to...</font>

313
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:10,830
<font color="yellow">what you have.</font>

314
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:12,870
<font color="yellow">During the next creditors' meeting﻿,</font>

315
00:21:12,870 --> 00:21:15,800
<font color="yellow">a voting will take place on the extension of the bonds.</font>

316
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:19,500
<font color="yellow">I have about 30 percent in bonds.</font>

317
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:23,830
<font color="yellow">You have to persuade the others to get the majority to vote.</font>

318
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:27,630
<font color="yellow">I'll be supporting you.</font>

319
00:21:27,630 --> 00:21:32,130
<font color="yellow">Are you telling me to secure the other 20 percent myself?</font>

320
00:21:32,130 --> 00:21:35,160
<font color="yellow">Then did you think that things would...</font>

321
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,600
<font color="yellow">automatically sort out?</font>

322
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:41,660
<font color="yellow">If the majority votes for you,</font>

323
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:45,930
<font color="yellow">I'll pass over the bonds and give you the loan as well.</font>

324
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:52,330
<font color="yellow">You're trying to test me.</font>

325
00:21:52,330 --> 00:21:54,460
<font color="yellow">This is a huge bet for me.</font>

326
00:21:54,460 --> 00:21:56,900
<font color="yellow">I should at least test you.</font>

327
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:00,400
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

328
00:22:01,030 --> 00:22:04,900
<font color="yellow">I'll get the majority on my side before the creditors' meeting.</font>

329
00:22:05,730 --> 00:22:07,360
<font color="yellow">It won't be easy.</font>

330
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:10,500
<font color="yellow">Most of them are on Chairman Do Choong's side.</font>

331
00:22:10,900 --> 00:22:13,330
<font color="yellow">Ms Do will help me.</font>

332
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:15,800
<font color="yellow">- Isn't that right?
-  What?</font>

333
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:18,730
<font color="yellow">Yes, of course.</font>

334
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,560
<font color="yellow">I'm not sure.</font>

335
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:25,560
<font color="yellow">I just hope Vice Chairman Do will sit still.</font>

336
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:42,530
<font color="yellow">You heard him, right?</font>

337
00:22:42,530 --> 00:22:45,100
<font color="yellow">Yes. About making me into the chairwoman?</font>

338
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:48,170
<font color="yellow">Not that.</font>

339
00:22:48,170 --> 00:22:50,410
<font color="yellow">We have to persuade 20 percent of the creditors.</font>

340
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:53,000
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, I'll help you.</font>

341
00:22:53,530 --> 00:22:55,700
<font color="yellow">We better meet the creditors right away.</font>

342
00:22:55,700 --> 00:22:59,330
<font color="yellow">Please set meetings with the ones that will be easier to persuade.</font>

343
00:22:59,330 --> 00:23:00,360
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

344
00:23:09,130 --> 00:23:11,900
<font color="yellow">- Gi Tan met with Chainsaw So?
-  Yes.</font>

345
00:23:12,730 --> 00:23:15,130
<font color="yellow">He even took Shin Young with him.</font>

346
00:23:15,530 --> 00:23:19,070
<font color="yellow">Doesn't this mean Chainsaw So is siding with him?</font>

347
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:20,800
<font color="yellow">Find out where Chainsaw So is right now.</font>

348
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,300
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

349
00:23:32,760 --> 00:23:33,830
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

350
00:23:36,860 --> 00:23:38,600
<font color="yellow">Hello, Vice Chairman Do.</font>

351
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,530
<font color="yellow">If you didn't eat yet, why don't you join me?</font>

352
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:42,430
<font color="yellow">I ate.</font>

353
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:45,800
<font color="yellow">I've been coming to this place for 30 years now.</font>

354
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:49,530
<font color="yellow">I almost lost it to Kang Gi Tan.</font>

355
00:23:49,530 --> 00:23:51,230
<font color="yellow">Why did you see him?</font>

356
00:23:52,830 --> 00:23:56,230
<font color="yellow">Did you promise him your bonds?</font>

357
00:23:58,760 --> 00:23:59,860
<font color="yellow">Not yet.</font>

358
00:23:59,860 --> 00:24:02,500
<font color="yellow">That means there's a possibility.</font>

359
00:24:03,060 --> 00:24:06,200
<font color="yellow">I'll see at the next creditors' meeting.</font>

360
00:24:06,630 --> 00:24:08,330
<font color="yellow">That's not what you promised.</font>

361
00:24:08,330 --> 00:24:09,400
<font color="yellow">Do you...</font>

362
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:12,570
<font color="yellow">still believe in promises?</font>

363
00:24:12,570 --> 00:24:16,960
<font color="yellow">I don't believe in anything without a signature.</font>

364
00:24:18,230 --> 00:24:22,230
<font color="yellow">- Sir...
-  He'll be persuading the creditors.</font>

365
00:24:22,730 --> 00:24:24,600
<font color="yellow">You can try to stop him yourself.</font>

366
00:24:25,730 --> 00:24:28,200
<font color="yellow">I'm going to root for Gi Tan.</font>

367
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:31,960
<font color="yellow">If 20 percent or more support him...</font>

368
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:34,830
<font color="yellow">along with my 30 percent,</font>

369
00:24:35,330 --> 00:24:36,430
<font color="yellow">Dodo Group...</font>

370
00:24:36,930 --> 00:24:38,540
<font color="yellow">will be in trouble.</font>

371
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:40,710
<font color="yellow">What if I block the majority?</font>

372
00:24:40,710 --> 00:24:41,800
<font color="yellow">If that's the case,</font>

373
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:45,560
<font color="yellow">my 30 percent will be used on you.</font>

374
00:24:45,560 --> 00:24:46,560
<font color="yellow">When that happens,</font>

375
00:24:46,900 --> 00:24:50,830
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan won't ever get a chance to step into this world.</font>

376
00:24:52,430 --> 00:24:56,000
<font color="yellow">Are you saying that you trust Gi Tan more than me?</font>

377
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:00,060
<font color="yellow">No, I don't trust either of you.</font>

378
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,230
<font color="yellow">But what can I do?</font>

379
00:25:01,660 --> 00:25:05,360
<font color="yellow">I'll have to push out the one I trust even less.</font>

380
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,900
<font color="yellow">Get the list of the creditors...</font>

381
00:25:16,900 --> 00:25:18,980
<font color="yellow">and set meetings in the order of percentage.</font>

382
00:25:18,980 --> 00:25:20,190
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

383
00:25:20,190 --> 00:25:24,030
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan already secured Chainsaw So's 30 percent.</font>

384
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:25,360
<font color="yellow">How is this going to work?</font>

385
00:25:25,360 --> 00:25:28,660
<font color="yellow">I have to try my best until the creditors' meeting.</font>

386
00:25:33,360 --> 00:25:35,360
<font color="yellow">You won't extend the bonds?</font>

387
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:38,150
<font color="yellow">- No.
-  I'm against it.</font>

388
00:25:38,150 --> 00:25:40,460
<font color="yellow">How is it any good for us if Dodo Group goes under?</font>

389
00:25:40,460 --> 00:25:42,430
<font color="yellow">The company won't be ruined.</font>

390
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:46,760
<font color="yellow">I'm saying we'll revive the company through some restructuring.</font>

391
00:25:46,760 --> 00:25:48,160
<font color="yellow">Chairman Kang.</font>

392
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:50,600
<font color="yellow">How much bonds do you have right now?</font>

393
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:52,330
<font color="yellow">Over 30 percent.</font>

394
00:25:52,330 --> 00:25:54,260
<font color="yellow">Do you think we're blind?</font>

395
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:57,200
<font color="yellow">I believe you only have 6 to 7 percent.</font>

396
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:06,060
<font color="yellow">(Chairman So)</font>

397
00:26:08,900 --> 00:26:10,760
<font color="yellow">Chairman Kang. What is it?</font>

398
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:13,830
<font color="yellow">Shouldn't I get you to sign a contract...</font>

399
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:16,440
<font color="yellow">to support me during the next creditors' meeting?</font>

400
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:18,960
<font color="yellow">You're as doubtful as me, aren't you?</font>

401
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:22,900
<font color="yellow">I love contracts, that's all.</font>

402
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:25,500
<font color="yellow">Come any time. I'll sign it for you.</font>

403
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:27,160
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

404
00:26:31,060 --> 00:26:33,730
<font color="yellow">You all know that Chairman So Gil Du...</font>

405
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,230
<font color="yellow">has over 30 percent in bonds, right?</font>

406
00:26:42,430 --> 00:26:43,760
<font color="yellow">That Gi Tan...</font>

407
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:46,230
<font color="yellow">He's borrowing my power...</font>

408
00:26:46,230 --> 00:26:48,060
<font color="yellow">to grab this golden opportunity.</font>

409
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:56,560
<font color="yellow">Even if that's the case,</font>

410
00:26:57,100 --> 00:26:58,930
<font color="yellow">we're loyal to the Do family.</font>

411
00:26:59,730 --> 00:27:01,700
<font color="yellow">We can't betray them overnight.</font>

412
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:05,630
<font color="yellow">- Why is she so late?
-  She'll be here soon.</font>

413
00:27:09,330 --> 00:27:11,000
<font color="yellow">CEO Do Shin Young is here.</font>

414
00:27:18,760 --> 00:27:20,030
<font color="yellow">Long time no see.</font>

415
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,200
<font color="yellow">How are you?</font>

416
00:27:22,630 --> 00:27:25,400
<font color="yellow">Do you even know what this is about?</font>

417
00:27:26,530 --> 00:27:29,590
<font color="yellow">I came because Chairman Kang asked me. Should I leave?</font>

418
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:30,600
<font color="yellow">Then...</font>

419
00:27:31,460 --> 00:27:34,930
<font color="yellow">Do you support Chairman Kang?</font>

420
00:27:35,300 --> 00:27:37,760
<font color="yellow">You all know what a mess my family is in.</font>

421
00:27:38,130 --> 00:27:39,560
<font color="yellow">The company is my priority.</font>

422
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:41,430
<font color="yellow">In order to save it,</font>

423
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:44,960
<font color="yellow">I believe Chairman Kang's plan is the right way.</font>

424
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:55,530
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan is securing more creditors.</font>

425
00:27:56,530 --> 00:27:59,730
<font color="yellow">He seems to be doing well since he has Shin Young on his side.</font>

426
00:28:00,100 --> 00:28:01,310
<font color="yellow">Is she crazy?</font>

427
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:04,300
<font color="yellow">I warned her, and yet she's still helping him?</font>

