00:28:05,130 --> 00:28:08,030
<font color="yellow">I've never considered Shin Young...</font>

429
00:28:08,030 --> 00:28:09,630
<font color="yellow">in my predictions.</font>

430
00:28:10,560 --> 00:28:12,000
<font color="yellow">How is it looking on Gun Woo's side?</font>

431
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:16,830
<font color="yellow">He's meeting with creditors with more bonds.</font>

432
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:20,700
<font color="yellow">Since Chainsaw So is supporting Gi Tan,</font>

433
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,560
<font color="yellow">he's at a disadvantage.</font>

434
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:26,700
<font color="yellow">Shouldn't you help Gun Woo?</font>

435
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:30,860
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo or Gi Tan, it's all the same to me.</font>

436
00:28:30,860 --> 00:28:34,200
<font color="yellow">You can't leave Gi Tan to take over Dodo Group.</font>

437
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:36,700
<font color="yellow">If I bring Chainsaw So to my side,</font>

438
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:39,830
<font color="yellow">I could be the winner of this battle.</font>

439
00:28:40,500 --> 00:28:42,960
<font color="yellow">Are you saying you'll try to take over Dodo Group?</font>

440
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:44,330
<font color="yellow">Chainsaw So...</font>

441
00:28:45,300 --> 00:28:48,000
<font color="yellow">isn't going to be easy to persuade.</font>

442
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:52,100
<font color="yellow">I'll have to offer him a better deal than Gi Tan did.</font>

443
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:04,130
<font color="yellow">You have a visitor.</font>

444
00:29:04,530 --> 00:29:05,660
<font color="yellow">Who is it?</font>

445
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:08,400
<font color="yellow">It's the ex-Seoul mayor candidate, Byun Il Jae.</font>

446
00:29:10,830 --> 00:29:12,430
<font color="yellow">I'm telling you this just in case.</font>

447
00:29:13,300 --> 00:29:16,080
<font color="yellow">If a man named Byun Il Jae comes to you, don't see him.</font>

448
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:18,580
<font color="yellow">Is he interested in Dodo Group as well?</font>

449
00:29:18,580 --> 00:29:20,200
<font color="yellow">He's a greedy person.</font>

450
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:25,030
<font color="yellow">I'm sure he'll be drooling somewhere.</font>

451
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,160
<font color="yellow">Should I bring him in?</font>

452
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,400
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

453
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:32,630
<font color="yellow">I'll go outside to see him.</font>

454
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:48,300
<font color="yellow">I'm So Gil Du. What is this about?</font>

455
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:51,460
<font color="yellow">Nice to meet you. I'm Byun Il Jae.</font>

456
00:29:52,430 --> 00:29:53,630
<font color="yellow">I know you very well.</font>

457
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:56,700
<font color="yellow">I voted you for Seoul Mayor...</font>

458
00:29:57,230 --> 00:29:58,700
<font color="yellow">and almost wanted to cut off my hand.</font>

459
00:30:01,100 --> 00:30:02,200
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

460
00:30:04,730 --> 00:30:08,000
<font color="yellow">Actually, I have something...</font>

461
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:10,000
<font color="yellow">I'd like to discuss with you.</font>

462
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:13,960
<font color="yellow">Kang Gi Tan told me you'd come to see me.</font>

463
00:30:14,500 --> 00:30:16,300
<font color="yellow">He asked me to give this to you.</font>

464
00:30:25,900 --> 00:30:28,730
<font color="yellow">What do you think you're doing, Old Man?</font>

465
00:30:28,730 --> 00:30:31,530
<font color="yellow">It's best to put salt on things that smell fishy.</font>

466
00:30:31,530 --> 00:30:32,730
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

467
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:34,900
<font color="yellow">Let go of me!</font>

468
00:30:34,900 --> 00:30:37,700
<font color="yellow">Don't obstruct my business!</font>

469
00:30:37,700 --> 00:30:38,730
<font color="yellow">Get out of here.</font>

470
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:40,600
<font color="yellow">How dare you?</font>

471
00:30:40,930 --> 00:30:42,980
<font color="yellow">Let go of me.</font>

472
00:30:42,980 --> 00:30:44,200
<font color="yellow">Lock the gate, Do Chi.</font>

473
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:49,200
<font color="yellow">What...</font>

474
00:30:52,100 --> 00:30:53,160
<font color="yellow">Are you okay?</font>

475
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:00,840
<font color="yellow">He threw salt at Il Jae?</font>

476
00:31:00,840 --> 00:31:01,900
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

477
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:05,730
<font color="yellow">I think Gi Tan got to Chainsaw So first.</font>

478
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,230
<font color="yellow">Shouldn't you...</font>

479
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:11,830
<font color="yellow">cut Il Jae off?</font>

480
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,500
<font color="yellow">I can't lose...</font>

481
00:31:14,100 --> 00:31:16,940
<font color="yellow">a financial backer so close to the general election.</font>

482
00:31:16,940 --> 00:31:19,500
<font color="yellow">Didn't Gi Tan say he'd help you?</font>

483
00:31:20,930 --> 00:31:22,130
<font color="yellow">Dirty money...</font>

484
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:25,130
<font color="yellow">can be spent wisely.</font>

485
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:29,460
<font color="yellow">Dangerous money, however, you must never touch.</font>

486
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:33,180
<font color="yellow">Il Jae's money is just as dangerous.</font>

487
00:31:33,180 --> 00:31:34,530
<font color="yellow">I can...</font>

488
00:31:34,530 --> 00:31:36,630
<font color="yellow">get rid of Il Jae at any time.</font>

489
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:39,600
<font color="yellow">But once I let Gi Tan control me,</font>

490
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:43,260
<font color="yellow">he will cause problems for me...</font>

491
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:45,700
<font color="yellow">even after I become the president.</font>

492
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:49,230
<font color="yellow">Thank you for your support, Mr Park.</font>

493
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:51,700
<font color="yellow">I'm trusting you...</font>

494
00:31:52,100 --> 00:31:55,070
<font color="yellow">because of Chairman So and Ms Do.</font>

495
00:31:55,070 --> 00:31:56,200
<font color="yellow">Did you hear that?</font>

496
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,000
<font color="yellow">I'm this influential.</font>

497
00:31:58,600 --> 00:32:00,160
<font color="yellow">I'll see you at the creditors' meeting.</font>

498
00:32:05,030 --> 00:32:06,130
<font color="yellow">See you soon.</font>

499
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:07,560
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

500
00:32:14,730 --> 00:32:16,570
<font color="yellow">All right. Who's next?</font>

501
00:32:16,570 --> 00:32:18,430
<font color="yellow">I'll persuade them all.</font>

502
00:32:18,830 --> 00:32:20,300
<font color="yellow">That's all for today.</font>

503
00:32:20,760 --> 00:32:21,760
<font color="yellow">You did well.</font>

504
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:24,200
<font color="yellow">Can I go now?</font>

505
00:32:25,130 --> 00:32:26,130
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

506
00:32:33,900 --> 00:32:35,700
<font color="yellow">Don't you think she's changed?</font>

507
00:32:36,900 --> 00:32:39,200
<font color="yellow">She's been acting strange lately.</font>

508
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,360
<font color="yellow">On any other day,</font>

509
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:43,160
<font color="yellow">she'd have bugged me to have a drink with her.</font>

510
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,600
<font color="yellow">Do you think something's wrong?</font>

511
00:32:54,460 --> 00:32:55,460
<font color="yellow">Ga Din.</font>

512
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,000
<font color="yellow">Why are you back?</font>

513
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:03,960
<font color="yellow">Won't you praise me for doing a good job today?</font>

514
00:33:04,760 --> 00:33:06,660
<font color="yellow">- Well done.
-  Is that it?</font>

515
00:33:07,800 --> 00:33:08,800
<font color="yellow">Kiss me.</font>

516
00:33:19,360 --> 00:33:20,400
<font color="yellow">Shin Young.</font>

517
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:24,360
<font color="yellow">Do you know what it means when a man and a woman kiss?</font>

518
00:33:24,860 --> 00:33:26,900
<font color="yellow">You like official seals.</font>

519
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:29,700
<font color="yellow">So do I. Consider this a seal of sorts.</font>

520
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:31,100
<font color="yellow">Go on.</font>

521
00:33:33,130 --> 00:33:34,130
<font color="yellow">Close your eyes.</font>

522
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:36,680
<font color="yellow">So you can run away again?</font>

523
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:39,330
<font color="yellow">I won't run away. I'm just shy.</font>

524
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:54,930
<font color="yellow">Open your eyes.</font>

525
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:58,660
<font color="yellow">- How was it?
-  Dreamy.</font>

526
00:33:59,730 --> 00:34:02,260
<font color="yellow">Don't ask me to kiss you over this again.</font>

527
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,560
<font color="yellow">I understand why...</font>

528
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:18,160
<font color="yellow">you're pushing me away.</font>

529
00:34:21,330 --> 00:34:22,600
<font color="yellow">(Dodo Group Creditors)</font>

530
00:34:22,600 --> 00:34:25,600
<font color="yellow">I marked Gi Tan's supporters in red.</font>

531
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:30,060
<font color="yellow">I think he has over 50 percent already.</font>

532
00:34:38,700 --> 00:34:41,130
<font color="yellow">We might lose before they even vote.</font>

533
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:42,830
<font color="yellow">We need...</font>

534
00:34:42,830 --> 00:34:45,760
<font color="yellow">to prevent Chainsaw So from attending the meeting.</font>

535
00:34:47,100 --> 00:34:49,030
<font color="yellow">We can't abduct him.</font>

536
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:52,130
<font color="yellow">There is a way.</font>

537
00:34:53,730 --> 00:34:56,370
<font color="yellow">Do you know what loan sharks like me...</font>

538
00:34:56,370 --> 00:34:58,200
<font color="yellow">fear the most?</font>

539
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:03,130
<font color="yellow">People from the police's Private Loan Task Force.</font>

540
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:05,950
<font color="yellow">The Private Loan Task Force?</font>

541
00:35:05,950 --> 00:35:07,000
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

542
00:35:08,970 --> 00:35:10,470
<font color="yellow">If they get to him,</font>

543
00:35:10,470 --> 00:35:13,500
<font color="yellow">even Chainsaw So will have a hard time getting free.</font>

544
00:35:14,560 --> 00:35:16,630
<font color="yellow">I know one of the managers.</font>

545
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:18,500
<font color="yellow">Shall I set up a meeting?</font>

546
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:22,170
<font color="yellow">Chainsaw So is connected to many politicians.</font>

547
00:35:22,170 --> 00:35:24,700
<font color="yellow">If Gi Tan puts pressure through the Chinese Embassy,</font>

548
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:26,560
<font color="yellow">he'll easily get out.</font>

549
00:35:27,500 --> 00:35:30,130
<font color="yellow">Set up a meeting with that manager.</font>

550
00:35:30,470 --> 00:35:31,800
<font color="yellow">Will you go for it?</font>

551
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:35,130
<font color="yellow">There's no other way but to push ahead.</font>

552
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:41,330
<font color="yellow">Whom are you calling?</font>

553
00:35:42,970 --> 00:35:45,600
<font color="yellow">Mr Hwang. I'm Vice Chairman Do Gun Woo.</font>

554
00:35:46,560 --> 00:35:48,800
<font color="yellow">I forgot about Hwang Jae Man.</font>

555
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:51,480
<font color="yellow">I'd like to meet you urgently.</font>

556
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:53,200
<font color="yellow">I will come and see you.</font>

557
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:13,160
<font color="yellow">Thank you for sparing the time.</font>

558
00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:17,560
<font color="yellow">I happen to have plans to meet someone else here.</font>

559
00:36:18,470 --> 00:36:19,600
<font color="yellow">What time is it?</font>

560
00:36:19,930 --> 00:36:21,730
<font color="yellow">You have an hour, Sir.</font>

561
00:36:22,300 --> 00:36:23,980
<font color="yellow">That's more than enough.</font>

562
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:25,000
<font color="yellow">First...</font>

563
00:36:28,030 --> 00:36:29,400
<font color="yellow">Read this, Sir.</font>

564
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:35,100
<font color="yellow">(Joint Name Contract)</font>

565
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:42,980
<font color="yellow">That proves that I'm...</font>

566
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:45,380
<font color="yellow">a joint owner of Z Capital's funds.</font>

567
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:46,400
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

568
00:36:47,830 --> 00:36:49,270
<font color="yellow">Il Jae...</font>

569
00:36:49,270 --> 00:36:51,440
<font color="yellow">didn't mention this to me.</font>

570
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:53,730
<font color="yellow">I thought so, which is why I showed you that.</font>

571
00:36:53,730 --> 00:36:55,970
<font color="yellow">Let me explain what that means.</font>

572
00:36:56,860 --> 00:36:58,700
<font color="yellow">Without my permission,</font>

573
00:36:59,030 --> 00:37:01,860
<font color="yellow">you cannot spend a single dime on your election campaign.</font>

574
00:37:04,860 --> 00:37:06,530
<font color="yellow">Do me one favour...</font>

575
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:08,500
<font color="yellow">and I will personally...</font>

576
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:10,400
<font color="yellow">fund your campaign.</font>

577
00:37:18,860 --> 00:37:20,030
<font color="yellow">What do you want?</font>

578
00:37:21,700 --> 00:37:22,760
<font color="yellow">At the creditors' meeting,</font>

579
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:24,330
<font color="yellow">a man called So Gil Du...</font>

580
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,600
<font color="yellow">will be under inspection.</font>

581
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:30,470
<font color="yellow">I need you to stop him from using his connections.</font>

582
00:37:30,970 --> 00:37:32,360
<font color="yellow">You want him...</font>

583
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:35,530
<font color="yellow">to stay away from the creditors' meeting.</font>

584
00:37:36,100 --> 00:37:37,370
<font color="yellow">That's right.</font>

585
00:37:37,370 --> 00:37:39,300
<font color="yellow">You'll also have to stop Gi Tan...</font>

586
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:41,760
<font color="yellow">from putting pressure through the Chinese Embassy.</font>

587
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:46,430
<font color="yellow">This is only until the meeting is over.</font>

588
00:37:46,930 --> 00:37:49,560
<font color="yellow">It's nothing for a man like you.</font>

589
00:37:50,100 --> 00:37:51,160
<font color="yellow">In exchange for that,</font>

590
00:37:52,100 --> 00:37:53,760
<font color="yellow">I want you to release...</font>

591
00:37:54,600 --> 00:37:55,600
<font color="yellow">Il Jae's funds.</font>

592
00:37:57,970 --> 00:37:59,060
<font color="yellow">I can't do that.</font>

593
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:04,210
<font color="yellow">I will fund your campaign with my own funds.</font>

594
00:38:04,210 --> 00:38:05,860
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about that.</font>

595
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:12,160
<font color="yellow">I need to think about it.</font>

596
00:38:12,970 --> 00:38:14,230
<font color="yellow">I'll call you.</font>

597
00:38:14,700 --> 00:38:15,760
<font color="yellow">There's no time.</font>

598
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:17,600
<font color="yellow">I need your answer today.</font>

599
00:38:28,330 --> 00:38:29,630
<font color="yellow">Oh dear.</font>

600
00:38:30,900 --> 00:38:32,100
<font color="yellow">Hello, Sir.</font>

601
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:34,600
<font color="yellow">Il Jae.</font>

602
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,760
<font color="yellow">You were right.</font>

603
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:40,130
<font color="yellow">He used your joint name contract...</font>

604
00:38:40,130 --> 00:38:41,970
<font color="yellow">to ask me for a favour.</font>

605
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:44,400
<font color="yellow">What was his request?</font>

606
00:38:50,970 --> 00:38:54,000
<font color="yellow">I can't tell from his facial expression alone.</font>

607
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:56,780
<font color="yellow">Where's the task force manager?</font>

608
00:38:56,780 --> 00:38:58,100
<font color="yellow">He's on his way.</font>

609
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:03,660
<font color="yellow">Do as Gun Woo asks, Sir.</font>

610
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,400
<font color="yellow">Will you help him?</font>

611
00:39:06,470 --> 00:39:09,160
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo and Gi Tan's fight is a great opportunity.</font>

612
00:39:10,130 --> 00:39:11,630
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, Sir.</font>

613
00:39:12,200 --> 00:39:13,830
<font color="yellow">Once the creditors' meeting's over,</font>

614
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:16,730
<font color="yellow">I will have full control of Dodo Group.</font>

615
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,630
<font color="yellow">That man...</font>

616
00:39:21,630 --> 00:39:24,970
<font color="yellow">The man they call Chainsaw or Hacksaw So.</font>

617
00:39:24,970 --> 00:39:26,660
<font color="yellow">Get me a list of...</font>

618
00:39:26,970 --> 00:39:28,130
<font color="yellow">his backers.</font>

619
00:39:30,060 --> 00:39:33,180
<font color="yellow">And set up a meeting with the ambassador from China.</font>

620
00:39:33,180 --> 00:39:34,300
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

621
00:39:46,470 --> 00:39:47,700
<font color="yellow">Hello, Sir.</font>

622
00:39:47,700 --> 00:39:48,930
<font color="yellow">Your request.</font>

623
00:39:49,730 --> 00:39:50,900
<font color="yellow">I'll do it.</font>

624
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:53,980
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

625
00:39:53,980 --> 00:39:55,030
<font color="yellow">In return,</font>

626
00:39:55,660 --> 00:39:58,000
<font color="yellow">I expect you to keep your promise.</font>

627
00:39:58,500 --> 00:39:59,560
<font color="yellow">I will.</font>

628
00:40:01,860 --> 00:40:02,930
<font color="yellow">Did he say yes?</font>

629
00:40:06,230 --> 00:40:07,230
<font color="yellow">We did it.</font>

630
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:16,660
<font color="yellow">Sir. Do you feel better?</font>

631
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:22,830
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

632
00:40:23,500 --> 00:40:24,500
<font color="yellow">What...</font>

633
00:40:25,660 --> 00:40:27,330
<font color="yellow">am I doing here?</font>

634
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:29,600
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

635
00:40:31,970 --> 00:40:33,000
<font color="yellow">Do I...</font>

636
00:40:34,660 --> 00:40:36,860
<font color="yellow">have an illness?</font>

637
00:40:38,330 --> 00:40:40,530
<font color="yellow">You have dementia.</font>

638
00:40:42,470 --> 00:40:43,500
<font color="yellow">Dementia?</font>

639
00:40:44,030 --> 00:40:45,600
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, Father.</font>

640
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:48,060
<font color="yellow">You'll get better if you receive treatment.</font>

641
00:40:51,930 --> 00:40:52,930
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh.</font>

642
00:40:54,560 --> 00:40:55,730
<font color="yellow">What about my will?</font>

643
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:59,930
<font color="yellow">You can make it once you recover.</font>

644
00:41:00,930 --> 00:41:02,030
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

645
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:04,160
<font color="yellow">I'll do that.</font>

646
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:06,860
<font color="yellow">You need intensive care.</font>

647
00:41:06,860 --> 00:41:09,500
<font color="yellow">I think you should stay here.</font>

648
00:41:10,260 --> 00:41:11,560
<font color="yellow">I agree.</font>

649
00:41:15,230 --> 00:41:16,260
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

650
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:18,830
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

651
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:23,360
<font color="yellow">I can't move my limbs!</font>

652
00:41:24,030 --> 00:41:26,300
<font color="yellow">I'll massage them for you.</font>

653
00:41:32,630 --> 00:41:33,700
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

654
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:35,930
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

655
00:41:37,730 --> 00:41:39,000
<font color="yellow">I think...</font>

656
00:41:41,500 --> 00:41:42,800
<font color="yellow">it's over for me.</font>

657
00:41:44,330 --> 00:41:45,600
<font color="yellow">You should...</font>

658
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:49,060
<font color="yellow">take over Dodo and...</font>

659
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:50,610
<font color="yellow">Please stay strong.</font>

660
00:41:50,610 --> 00:41:52,900
<font color="yellow">I can't live without you, Father.</font>

661
00:41:56,430 --> 00:41:58,000
<font color="yellow">You can beat this.</font>

662
00:41:58,400 --> 00:42:01,660
<font color="yellow">You went through physical therapy and managed to walk again.</font>

663
00:42:02,560 --> 00:42:03,700
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

664
00:42:04,830 --> 00:42:08,130
<font color="yellow">I will make you better.</font>

665
00:42:08,530 --> 00:42:09,660
<font color="yellow">Trust me.</font>

666
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:37,730
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

667
00:42:54,830 --> 00:42:56,430
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Soo Yeon,</font>

668
00:42:56,430 --> 00:42:58,400
<font color="yellow">for lying to him for me.</font>

669
00:42:59,470 --> 00:43:03,130
<font color="yellow">If he's losing control of his arms and legs...</font>

670
00:43:03,130 --> 00:43:05,000
<font color="yellow">He has less than six months.</font>

671
00:43:06,130 --> 00:43:07,930
<font color="yellow">It's terminal.</font>

672
00:43:11,930 --> 00:43:13,830
<font color="yellow">You should go home. It's late.</font>

673
00:43:14,900 --> 00:43:16,360
<font color="yellow">Will you stay?</font>

674
00:43:17,130 --> 00:43:18,970
<font color="yellow">I should stay with him.</font>

675
00:43:19,860 --> 00:43:22,600
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry I can't take you home.</font>

676
00:44:15,460 --> 00:44:16,700
<font color="yellow">Let's get engaged.</font>

677
00:44:18,430 --> 00:44:20,130
<font color="yellow">Before your father passes.</font>

678
00:44:32,060 --> 00:44:33,060
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

679
00:44:34,160 --> 00:44:35,760
<font color="yellow">I took too long to answer.</font>

680
00:45:19,830 --> 00:45:21,830
<font color="yellow">(Dodo Group)</font>

681
00:45:24,800 --> 00:45:27,460
<font color="yellow">Sir, the Private Loan Task Force...</font>

682
00:45:27,460 --> 00:45:29,160
<font color="yellow">just left for Chainsaw So's house.</font>

683
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:34,600
<font color="yellow">You're early.</font>

684
00:45:35,060 --> 00:45:37,100
<font color="yellow">I'm meeting the creditors before the meeting.</font>

685
00:45:37,100 --> 00:45:39,330
<font color="yellow">You look pretty confident.</font>

686
00:45:39,330 --> 00:45:42,260
<font color="yellow">Why put on a show when we both know the other's hand?</font>

687
00:45:42,900 --> 00:45:46,400
<font color="yellow">We have 58 percent, so you must have 42 percent.</font>

688
00:45:46,900 --> 00:45:50,300
<font color="yellow">The creditors' meeting is still three hours away.</font>

689
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:52,600
<font color="yellow">No one knows what will happen by then.</font>

690
00:45:52,600 --> 00:45:54,700
<font color="yellow">Everyone knows but you.</font>

691
00:45:57,630 --> 00:45:59,400
<font color="yellow">Shin Young, let's have a word.</font>

692
00:46:09,100 --> 00:46:13,230
<font color="yellow">Don't you know why he wants the matured bonds?</font>

693
00:46:13,730 --> 00:46:16,260
<font color="yellow">We'll go bankrupt if the creditors don't extend it.</font>

694
00:46:17,260 --> 00:46:18,360
<font color="yellow">I know that.</font>

695
00:46:18,960 --> 00:46:20,930
<font color="yellow">If you're still helping him,</font>

696
00:46:20,930 --> 00:46:23,430
<font color="yellow">that means you betrayed your father and the company.</font>

697
00:46:23,430 --> 00:46:24,900
<font color="yellow">I trust Gi Tan.</font>

698
00:46:24,900 --> 00:46:26,930
<font color="yellow">He won't ruin the company.</font>

699
00:46:26,930 --> 00:46:28,060
<font color="yellow">Shin Young.</font>

700
00:46:29,430 --> 00:46:32,400
<font color="yellow">You don't know what kind of person he is.</font>

701
00:46:32,400 --> 00:46:33,610
<font color="yellow">I know very well.</font>

702
00:46:33,610 --> 00:46:35,930
<font color="yellow">He almost died when you framed him for murder.</font>

703
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:41,030
<font color="yellow">I won't let Father accept and acknowledge someone like you.</font>

704
00:46:41,030 --> 00:46:42,740
<font color="yellow">That's why I'm helping him.</font>

705
00:46:42,740 --> 00:46:44,330
<font color="yellow">To get rid of you.</font>

706
00:46:45,130 --> 00:46:47,560
<font color="yellow">Do you know that Gwang Woo...</font>

707
00:46:47,560 --> 00:46:49,560
<font color="yellow">killed his parents?</font>

708
00:46:52,630 --> 00:46:54,400
<font color="yellow">- I do.
-  Then...</font>

709
00:46:54,400 --> 00:46:57,300
<font color="yellow">you must also know that Gi Tan's using you.</font>

710
00:46:59,230 --> 00:47:01,560
<font color="yellow">If he really wanted to use me,</font>

711
00:47:01,560 --> 00:47:04,430
<font color="yellow">he wouldn't have refused my wedding proposal.</font>

712
00:47:04,430 --> 00:47:07,600
<font color="yellow">He will not go back on his word.</font>

713
00:47:08,300 --> 00:47:10,100
<font color="yellow">He's not like you.</font>

714
00:47:10,830 --> 00:47:13,830
<font color="yellow">As soon as the meeting is over,</font>

715
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:16,630
<font color="yellow">I will have you ousted from the company.</font>

716
00:47:18,230 --> 00:47:19,530
<font color="yellow">Don't regret it then.</font>

717
00:47:37,930 --> 00:47:39,430
<font color="yellow">Who are you? Get out of here!</font>

718
00:47:40,430 --> 00:47:43,030
<font color="yellow">- Mr So Gil Du?
-  That would be me.</font>

719
00:47:43,900 --> 00:47:45,860
<font color="yellow">How dare you barge in here?</font>

720
00:47:46,430 --> 00:47:50,030
<font color="yellow">We're with the Private Loan Task Force.</font>

721
00:47:52,230 --> 00:47:54,960
<font color="yellow">You have no business with me.</font>

722
00:47:55,700 --> 00:47:56,830
<font color="yellow">We got a tip.</font>

723
00:47:59,430 --> 00:48:00,830
<font color="yellow">Our search and seizure warrant.</font>

724
00:48:01,260 --> 00:48:04,060
<font color="yellow">Where did you get the tip from?</font>

725
00:48:04,060 --> 00:48:05,060
<font color="yellow">Search the place.</font>

726
00:48:11,430 --> 00:48:12,830
<font color="yellow">You must come with us.</font>

727
00:48:14,200 --> 00:48:16,130
<font color="yellow">Are you with the police?</font>

728
00:48:16,700 --> 00:48:18,130
<font color="yellow">Let me make a call.</font>

729
00:48:21,100 --> 00:48:23,000
<font color="yellow">(Police Commissioner Lee)</font>

730
00:48:27,130 --> 00:48:30,000
<font color="yellow">The phone has been turned off. Please...</font>

731
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:32,560
<font color="yellow">Is he in a meeting?</font>

732
00:48:33,630 --> 00:48:35,400
<font color="yellow">(Police Commissioner Park)</font>

733
00:48:38,030 --> 00:48:42,500
<font color="yellow">The phone has been turned off. Please leave a message.</font>

734
00:48:57,300 --> 00:48:58,360
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

735
00:48:58,930 --> 00:49:01,800
<font color="yellow">No one's picking up. Something's wrong.</font>

736
00:49:01,800 --> 00:49:03,060
<font color="yellow">Is this deliberate?</font>

737
00:49:03,060 --> 00:49:05,630
<font color="yellow">It has to be. They'd never ignore my calls.</font>

738
00:49:06,030 --> 00:49:07,900
<font color="yellow">I'll ask Chairman Kang to help.</font>

739
00:49:07,900 --> 00:49:09,560
<font color="yellow">- Please do.
-  Get in.</font>

740
00:49:39,730 --> 00:49:40,890
<font color="yellow">Speak.</font>

741
00:49:40,890 --> 00:49:43,360
<font color="yellow">They just dragged Chainsaw So away.</font>

742
00:49:45,600 --> 00:49:46,860
<font color="yellow">Mr Moon.</font>

743
00:49:47,500 --> 00:49:50,230
<font color="yellow">The Private Loan Task Force just arrested Chairman So.</font>

744
00:49:52,130 --> 00:49:53,600
<font color="yellow">Well done, Mr Yang.</font>

745
00:49:54,930 --> 00:49:57,460
<font color="yellow">I think someone got them involved.</font>

746
00:50:00,560 --> 00:50:04,160
<font color="yellow">I'll go to the police station and get his power of attorney.</font>

747
00:50:06,230 --> 00:50:10,130
<font color="yellow">The meeting will have begun by the time you get it notarised.</font>

748
00:50:10,560 --> 00:50:12,660
<font color="yellow">You could call the Chinese Embassy...</font>

749
00:50:12,660 --> 00:50:14,360
<font color="yellow">and ask them to intervene.</font>

750
00:50:15,460 --> 00:50:16,600
<font color="yellow">I'll do that.</font>

751
00:50:18,830 --> 00:50:20,360
<font color="yellow">Is something wrong?</font>

752
00:50:20,360 --> 00:50:22,700
<font color="yellow">Chairman So just got arrested.</font>

753
00:50:22,700 --> 00:50:24,660
<font color="yellow">For illegal loans.</font>

754
00:50:26,700 --> 00:50:29,430
<font color="yellow">Are you behind this?</font>

755
00:50:30,200 --> 00:50:31,860
<font color="yellow">Don't blame me.</font>

756
00:50:31,860 --> 00:50:34,300
<font color="yellow">Blame Chainsaw So for his illegal business.</font>

757
00:50:36,830 --> 00:50:39,400
<font color="yellow">Wait, you can't talk to the Chinese Embassy about this.</font>

758
00:50:39,400 --> 00:50:40,800
<font color="yellow">It won't work this time.</font>

759
00:50:50,630 --> 00:50:51,630
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan.</font>

760
00:51:02,730 --> 00:51:04,630
<font color="yellow">(It's Chairman Kang.)</font>

761
00:51:04,630 --> 00:51:06,400
<font color="yellow">He says it's a call from Gi Tan.</font>

762
00:51:07,360 --> 00:51:10,300
<font color="yellow">If he feels too uncomfortable to take his call,</font>

763
00:51:10,660 --> 00:51:12,860
<font color="yellow">tell him that I can take it for him.</font>

764
00:51:14,000 --> 00:51:17,300
<font color="yellow">(If you don't want to take his call, Mr Hwang can take it for you.)</font>

765
00:51:17,300 --> 00:51:18,500
<font color="yellow">(Sure.)</font>

766
00:51:26,960 --> 00:51:28,350
<font color="yellow">(It's me, Kang Gi Tan.)</font>

767
00:51:28,350 --> 00:51:29,760
<font color="yellow">It's me, Hwang Jae Man.</font>

768
00:51:33,300 --> 00:51:34,600
<font color="yellow">Let me talk to Ambassador Wang.</font>

769
00:51:35,130 --> 00:51:38,430
<font color="yellow">Because of recent downfall in Sino-Korean relationship,</font>

770
00:51:39,130 --> 00:51:40,760
<font color="yellow">he feels a bit burdened...</font>

771
00:51:41,230 --> 00:51:43,160
<font color="yellow">to do you a favour.</font>

772
00:51:43,630 --> 00:51:44,660
<font color="yellow">Mr Hwang.</font>

773
00:51:45,500 --> 00:51:47,030
<font color="yellow">Are you siding with Gun Woo?</font>

774
00:51:47,530 --> 00:51:48,530
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

775
00:51:48,900 --> 00:51:50,400
<font color="yellow">I don't take any sides.</font>

776
00:51:50,900 --> 00:51:52,110
<font color="yellow">I'm hanging up.</font>

777
00:51:52,110 --> 00:51:54,830
<font color="yellow">I'm probably the only one who can take care of this.</font>

778
00:51:55,360 --> 00:51:57,700
<font color="yellow">Won't you even ask me for a favour?</font>

779
00:51:58,530 --> 00:52:02,070
<font color="yellow">You must not be too desperate.</font>

780
00:52:02,070 --> 00:52:04,430
<font color="yellow">I already know that you won't help me.</font>

781
00:52:04,900 --> 00:52:07,530
<font color="yellow">I don't like Gun Woo.</font>

782
00:52:08,400 --> 00:52:11,760
<font color="yellow">He's very impudent just like his father.</font>

783
00:52:12,130 --> 00:52:13,130
<font color="yellow">Does that mean...</font>

784
00:52:14,830 --> 00:52:17,130
<font color="yellow">you may help me?</font>

785
00:52:19,300 --> 00:52:20,960
<font color="yellow">That may happen.</font>

786
00:52:23,330 --> 00:52:25,500
<font color="yellow">Don't try to sound me out. Goodbye.</font>

787
00:52:27,730 --> 00:52:29,400
<font color="yellow">Who was that? My uncle?</font>

788
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:31,120
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

789
00:52:31,120 --> 00:52:32,660
<font color="yellow">You should've let me talk to him.</font>

790
00:52:32,660 --> 00:52:34,900
<font color="yellow">He may do this if I asked.</font>

791
00:52:34,900 --> 00:52:36,330
<font color="yellow">Even if you asked,</font>

792
00:52:36,930 --> 00:52:38,730
<font color="yellow">I doubt Mr Hwang will help me.</font>

793
00:52:39,930 --> 00:52:41,360
<font color="yellow">Yes, Commissioner Lee.</font>

794
00:52:42,000 --> 00:52:43,460
<font color="yellow">It's me, Jae Man.</font>

795
00:52:44,260 --> 00:52:45,880
<font color="yellow">Isn't there...</font>

796
00:52:45,880 --> 00:52:48,360
<font color="yellow">a team named Private Loan Task Force?</font>

797
00:52:49,760 --> 00:52:51,060
<font color="yellow">One of my friends...</font>

798
00:52:51,630 --> 00:52:53,000
<font color="yellow">named So Gil Du was...</font>

799
00:52:53,460 --> 00:52:55,700
<font color="yellow">just arrested by them.</font>

800
00:53:00,860 --> 00:53:01,860
<font color="yellow">Chairman So.</font>

801
00:53:02,830 --> 00:53:04,900
<font color="yellow">I guess the Chinese Embassy is powerful.</font>

802
00:53:04,900 --> 00:53:06,200
<font color="yellow">The Chinese Embassy?</font>

803
00:53:06,730 --> 00:53:08,700
<font color="yellow">I heard Jae Man let me out.</font>

804
00:53:10,260 --> 00:53:11,490
<font color="yellow">Is that true?</font>

805
00:53:11,490 --> 00:53:13,030
<font color="yellow">I heard it with my own ears.</font>

806
00:53:13,430 --> 00:53:15,300
<font color="yellow">I heard Jae Man let me out.</font>

807
00:53:23,200 --> 00:53:25,030
<font color="yellow">Your call cannot be connected.</font>

808
00:53:26,030 --> 00:53:28,470
<font color="yellow">He can't take your call because the meeting already began.</font>

809
00:53:28,470 --> 00:53:30,400
<font color="yellow">- Let's go.
-  Your call...</font>

810
00:53:30,400 --> 00:53:33,320
<font color="yellow">cannot be connected. Please leave your message...</font>

811
00:53:33,320 --> 00:53:34,800
<font color="yellow">This meeting is...</font>

812
00:53:35,130 --> 00:53:38,630
<font color="yellow">about renewing the contract of your matured bonds.</font>

813
00:53:39,230 --> 00:53:41,930
<font color="yellow">Please share your thoughts freely...</font>

814
00:53:42,400 --> 00:53:43,860
<font color="yellow">if you'd like to speak.</font>

815
00:53:49,630 --> 00:53:53,000
<font color="yellow">(Creditors' Meeting for Dodo Group)</font>

816
00:53:56,300 --> 00:53:57,300
<font color="yellow">I'd like to make...</font>

817
00:53:58,130 --> 00:53:59,760
<font color="yellow">a formal request to Dodo Group.</font>

818
00:54:00,730 --> 00:54:03,030
<font color="yellow">If you'd like a renewal of our contract,</font>

819
00:54:03,900 --> 00:54:05,130
<font color="yellow">you will have to change...</font>

820
00:54:06,130 --> 00:54:07,330
<font color="yellow">your holding company...</font>

821
00:54:08,130 --> 00:54:09,760
<font color="yellow">from Dodo Pharmaceutical to Dodo Hotel.</font>

822
00:54:20,000 --> 00:54:23,600
<font color="yellow">The current speaker is the second large shareholder of Dodo Hotel.</font>

823
00:54:24,030 --> 00:54:26,330
<font color="yellow">He's currently plotting a scheme with the largest shareholder,</font>

824
00:54:26,760 --> 00:54:29,430
<font color="yellow">CEO Do Shin Young, to take Dodo Group for themselves.</font>

825
00:54:29,900 --> 00:54:30,900
<font color="yellow">Vice President Do Gun Woo.</font>

826
00:54:32,200 --> 00:54:34,200
<font color="yellow">Didn't you recently inspect your subsidiaries?</font>

827
00:54:36,900 --> 00:54:39,500
<font color="yellow">This is a report of his inspection,</font>

828
00:54:40,100 --> 00:54:41,630
<font color="yellow">which I got a few days ago.</font>

829
00:54:42,930 --> 00:54:44,200
<font color="yellow">According to this report,</font>

830
00:54:44,830 --> 00:54:46,500
<font color="yellow">there are seven subsidiaries...</font>

831
00:54:47,130 --> 00:54:51,260
<font color="yellow">that have more accumulated deficit than their capital.</font>

832
00:54:54,530 --> 00:54:57,100
<font color="yellow">That means seven subsidiaries...</font>

833
00:54:57,430 --> 00:54:59,430
<font color="yellow">may go bankrupt within the year.</font>

834
00:55:02,560 --> 00:55:04,730
<font color="yellow">You may refute me if I'm wrong, Vice President Do.</font>

835
00:55:11,100 --> 00:55:12,660
<font color="yellow">Here is the most important fact.</font>

836
00:55:13,260 --> 00:55:16,100
<font color="yellow">Among the subsidiaries, the biggest deficit...</font>

837
00:55:16,100 --> 00:55:17,730
<font color="yellow">belongs to Dodo Pharmaceutical.</font>

838
00:55:17,730 --> 00:55:19,030
<font color="yellow">- What does that mean?
-  Dodo Pharmaceutical?</font>

839
00:55:20,730 --> 00:55:22,060
<font color="yellow">I tell you,</font>

840
00:55:22,560 --> 00:55:23,710
<font color="yellow">if this goes on,</font>

841
00:55:23,710 --> 00:55:26,060
<font color="yellow">no one sitting in this room...</font>

842
00:55:26,530 --> 00:55:29,330
<font color="yellow">will be able to get his or her principal back.</font>

843
00:55:31,760 --> 00:55:32,760
<font color="yellow">That's all.</font>

844
00:55:33,630 --> 00:55:35,500
<font color="yellow">- What?
-  That's absurd.</font>

845
00:55:55,360 --> 00:55:57,100
<font color="yellow">I applaud you for trying,</font>

846
00:55:57,100 --> 00:55:58,160
<font color="yellow">but it's already over.</font>

847
00:55:58,530 --> 00:56:00,430
<font color="yellow">I own 42 percent...</font>

848
00:56:01,130 --> 00:56:03,630
<font color="yellow">and you have 28 percent without Chainsaw So's shares.</font>

849
00:56:10,200 --> 00:56:11,800
<font color="yellow">And now,</font>

850
00:56:12,130 --> 00:56:14,210
<font color="yellow">we will vote yes or no...</font>

851
00:56:14,210 --> 00:56:16,200
<font color="yellow">on renewing the contract.</font>

852
00:56:16,930 --> 00:56:17,930
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

853
00:56:19,560 --> 00:56:22,830
<font color="yellow">Before we vote, someone would like to say a word.</font>

854
00:56:37,000 --> 00:56:38,160
<font color="yellow">I was...</font>

855
00:56:39,130 --> 00:56:42,260
<font color="yellow">just arrested by the police.</font>

856
00:56:44,460 --> 00:56:45,660
<font color="yellow">Someone here...</font>

857
00:56:46,460 --> 00:56:50,030
<font color="yellow">reported me for giving out illegal private loans.</font>

858
00:56:50,730 --> 00:56:53,430
<font color="yellow">Well, need I say more?</font>

859
00:56:54,000 --> 00:56:55,100
<font color="yellow">Let us...</font>

860
00:56:56,300 --> 00:56:57,360
<font color="yellow">vote.</font>

861
00:57:07,330 --> 00:57:08,860
<font color="yellow">Are you saying...</font>

862
00:57:09,430 --> 00:57:12,000
<font color="yellow">not Gi Tan or Gun Woo, but Il Jae will be taking it over?</font>

863
00:57:12,000 --> 00:57:14,500
<font color="yellow">Yes. If things go as he planned.</font>

864
00:57:14,900 --> 00:57:15,930
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

865
00:57:16,300 --> 00:57:18,000
<font color="yellow">Did you let Chainsaw So out...</font>

866
00:57:18,000 --> 00:57:19,360
<font color="yellow">not to help Gi Tan but...</font>

867
00:57:25,730 --> 00:57:27,930
<font color="yellow">I've taken Il Jae's side.</font>

868
00:57:43,560 --> 00:57:45,700
<font color="yellow">I will announce the result.</font>

869
00:57:48,660 --> 00:57:50,300
<font color="yellow">(Yes, No)</font>

870
00:57:52,930 --> 00:57:54,200
<font color="yellow">(Yes, No)</font>

871
00:57:56,730 --> 00:57:59,000
<font color="yellow">(Yes, No)</font>

872
00:58:28,200 --> 00:58:29,200
<font color="yellow">Just as I promised,</font>

873
00:58:29,730 --> 00:58:31,810
<font color="yellow">I will sell my bonds to you.</font>

874
00:58:31,810 --> 00:58:33,210
<font color="yellow">I need a loan, too.</font>

875
00:58:33,210 --> 00:58:35,070
<font color="yellow">Make sure you pay your interest.</font>

876
00:58:35,070 --> 00:58:36,100
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

877
00:58:36,630 --> 00:58:38,210
<font color="yellow">You should take him back home.</font>

878
00:58:38,210 --> 00:58:39,230
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

879
00:58:40,600 --> 00:58:41,600
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

880
00:58:45,360 --> 00:58:48,630
<font color="yellow">I do not understand why Jae Man took our side.</font>

881
00:58:48,630 --> 00:58:50,360
<font color="yellow">I'm sure he's up to something.</font>

882
00:58:51,130 --> 00:58:52,500
<font color="yellow">But I'm not sure what it is.</font>

883
00:58:53,430 --> 00:58:57,260
<font color="yellow">Who cares? Dodo Group is ours.</font>

884
00:58:59,030 --> 00:59:00,090
<font color="yellow">Soo Tak.</font>

885
00:59:00,090 --> 00:59:01,660
<font color="yellow">Will you take Shin Young back to the hotel?</font>

886
00:59:02,830 --> 00:59:03,900
<font color="yellow">Aren't you coming?</font>

887
00:59:04,260 --> 00:59:06,120
<font color="yellow">We should celebrate.</font>

888
00:59:06,120 --> 00:59:08,630
<font color="yellow">We'll celebrate later. You can go ahead, Shin Young.</font>

889
00:59:16,360 --> 00:59:17,400
<font color="yellow">Mr Moon.</font>

890
00:59:18,130 --> 00:59:19,130
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

891
00:59:20,630 --> 00:59:22,630
<font color="yellow">I am going to confess my love to Soo Yeon today.</font>

892
00:59:26,730 --> 00:59:28,330
<font color="yellow">I destroyed Gun Woo today.</font>

893
00:59:29,500 --> 00:59:31,360
<font color="yellow">You can't stop me any more.</font>

894
00:59:31,900 --> 00:59:33,260
<font color="yellow">I do not mind,</font>

895
00:59:33,930 --> 00:59:36,500
<font color="yellow">but I'm afraid your headache may start again.</font>

896
00:59:36,500 --> 00:59:38,060
<font color="yellow">I'd rather have that headache.</font>

897
00:59:40,460 --> 00:59:41,630
<font color="yellow">Whenever I see her,</font>

898
00:59:43,560 --> 00:59:45,130
<font color="yellow">my heart aches so much...</font>

899
00:59:45,660 --> 00:59:46,760
<font color="yellow">that I can't stand it.</font>

900
00:59:59,730 --> 01:00:01,960
<font color="yellow">Your fight against Gi Tan was...</font>

901
01:00:02,330 --> 01:00:03,930
<font color="yellow">very intriguing.</font>

902
01:00:06,500 --> 01:00:08,360
<font color="yellow">I thought you'd ask for my help,</font>

903
01:00:08,830 --> 01:00:10,660
<font color="yellow">but you went to Mr Hwang instead.</font>

904
01:00:14,560 --> 01:00:16,700
<font color="yellow">Do you see now, Gun Woo?</font>

905
01:00:16,700 --> 01:00:19,760
<font color="yellow">You can't win against Gi Tan without my help.</font>

906
01:00:20,130 --> 01:00:21,500
<font color="yellow">I want to be alone.</font>

907
01:00:22,200 --> 01:00:23,530
<font color="yellow">So please leave.</font>

908
01:00:28,100 --> 01:00:29,100
<font color="yellow">Don't change...</font>

909
01:00:29,830 --> 01:00:31,300
<font color="yellow">your holding company to Dodo Hotel.</font>

910
01:00:32,200 --> 01:00:35,710
<font color="yellow">In that case, Gi Tan will take out all of his matured bonds.</font>

911
01:00:35,710 --> 01:00:36,860
<font color="yellow">Let him do it.</font>

912
01:00:38,000 --> 01:00:42,360
<font color="yellow">We're in no financial position to prevent bankruptcy.</font>

913
01:00:43,260 --> 01:00:44,360
<font color="yellow">I have...</font>

914
01:00:45,260 --> 01:00:46,960
<font color="yellow">a plan.</font>

915
01:01:13,660 --> 01:01:14,760
<font color="yellow">You're late.</font>

916
01:01:15,730 --> 01:01:17,760
<font color="yellow">Why are you here?</font>

917
01:01:18,160 --> 01:01:20,000
<font color="yellow">I'd like to talk to you.</font>

918
01:01:21,000 --> 01:01:22,330
<font color="yellow">See you at home.</font>

919
01:01:25,830 --> 01:01:26,960
<font color="yellow">Let's go somewhere else.</font>

920
01:01:40,800 --> 01:01:41,900
<font color="yellow">What do you want to say?</font>

921
01:01:43,200 --> 01:01:44,630
<font color="yellow">A man...</font>

922
01:01:47,230 --> 01:01:49,000
<font color="yellow">fell in love three times.</font>

923
01:01:51,700 --> 01:01:54,100
<font color="yellow">Would you believe if I said it was with the same woman?</font>

924
01:01:56,930 --> 01:01:58,430
<font color="yellow">The first time,</font>

925
01:02:01,460 --> 01:02:03,830
<font color="yellow">the man was unable to see.</font>

926
01:02:07,560 --> 01:02:08,760
<font color="yellow">10 years later...</font>

927
01:02:10,760 --> 01:02:13,330
<font color="yellow">when he met her again after regaining his sight,</font>

928
01:02:16,630 --> 01:02:19,000
<font color="yellow">he didn't know she was the one he was looking for.</font>

929
01:02:21,560 --> 01:02:23,030
<font color="yellow">And he fell in love again.</font>

930
01:02:26,100 --> 01:02:27,260
<font color="yellow">Then the man...</font>

931
01:02:29,400 --> 01:02:30,930
<font color="yellow">lost his memory.</font>

932
01:02:33,360 --> 01:02:34,960
<font color="yellow">Being the fool he was,</font>

933
01:02:37,560 --> 01:02:39,730
<font color="yellow">he fell in love with her again.</font>

934
01:02:55,760 --> 01:02:56,800
<font color="yellow">Jeong Eun.</font>

935
01:02:59,830 --> 01:03:00,900
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

936
01:03:04,200 --> 01:03:05,360
<font color="yellow">Don't avoid me...</font>

937
01:03:08,730 --> 01:03:09,960
<font color="yellow">for the fear of hurting me.</font>

938
01:03:18,800 --> 01:03:19,900
<font color="yellow">This is the third time.</font>

939
01:03:21,760 --> 01:03:23,130
<font color="yellow">Even if I die,</font>

940
01:03:24,500 --> 01:03:25,960
<font color="yellow">I won't lose you again.</font>

941
01:04:01,130 --> 01:04:02,960
<font color="yellow">(Monster)</font>

942
01:04:02,960 --> 01:04:05,430
<font color="yellow">Things will become tense.</font>

943
01:04:05,430 --> 01:04:07,060
<font color="yellow">We must go on the offence.</font>

944
01:04:07,060 --> 01:04:08,800
<font color="yellow">Choong Dong isn't enough.</font>

945
01:04:08,800 --> 01:04:10,600
<font color="yellow">We need to shake Il Jae, too.</font>

946
01:04:10,600 --> 01:04:13,300
<font color="yellow">Listen to what I say very carefully.</font>

947
01:04:13,300 --> 01:04:15,330
<font color="yellow">I'll get the information you want.</font>

948
01:04:15,330 --> 01:04:17,930
<font color="yellow">You're in no position to make demands.</font>

949
01:04:17,930 --> 01:04:19,960
<font color="yellow">Please don't side with Il Jae.</font>

950
01:04:19,960 --> 01:04:21,630
<font color="yellow">Call the family.</font>

951
01:04:21,630 --> 01:04:23,560
<font color="yellow">It's time to close the deal.</font>

952
01:04:23,560 --> 01:04:24,730
<font color="yellow">See you tomorrow.</font>

